Package: TestWithRStudio
Type: Package
Title: Testing your R Package with RStudio in Continuous Integration
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Changcheng Li", email = "cxl508@psu.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: As an R package developer, have you met the situation that your package passes R CMD check but crashes RStudio?
    TestWithRStudio can help you deal with this situation by testing your R package with RStudio using continuous integration
    like Travis CI.
